import React from 'react'
import {
  ThemeProvider,
  theme,
  ColorModeProvider,
  CSSReset,
} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import './App.css'
import { Dashboard } from './pages'
import { MainLayout } from './Layouts'

const config = {
  initialColorMode: 'light',
}
const App = ({ Component }) => (
  <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
    <ColorModeProvider options={config}>
      <CSSReset />
      <MainLayout />
    </ColorModeProvider>
  </ThemeProvider>
)

export default App
